318
00:16:41,875 --> 00:16:43,041
[KANAME gasps]

319
00:16:43,125 --> 00:16:45,625
[SOUSUKE grunts]

320
00:16:45,708 --> 00:16:46,875
[KANAME gasps]

321
00:16:55,791 --> 00:17:01,041
Hey, Sousuke. Sousuke!
Sousuke Sagara!

322
00:17:05,250 --> 00:17:08,083
Hey, Sousuke, are you alright?

323
00:17:10,083 --> 00:17:12,416
[SOUSUKE] Yes.
There's nothing wrong with me.

324
00:17:12,500 --> 00:17:14,000
