325
00:17:14,083 --> 00:17:16,291
What on earth were you
thinking back there?!

326
00:17:16,375 --> 00:17:18,791
I just wanted to get out at
this station all of a sudden.

327
00:17:18,875 --> 00:17:21,083
It has nothing to
do with you, okay?

328
00:17:21,166 --> 00:17:23,500
So you mean to tell me
after all this time...?

329
00:17:23,583 --> 00:17:24,875
It's still a coincidence.

330
00:17:24,958 --> 00:17:27,500
[KANAME sighs]

331
00:17:32,416 --> 00:17:35,583
[KANAME sighs]

332
00:17:35,666 --> 00:17:38,625
