334
00:17:41,166 --> 00:17:43,500
[KANAME]
I can't take this anymore.

335
00:17:43,583 --> 00:17:44,875
Hmph!

336
00:17:51,000 --> 00:17:51,875
[KANAME]
Hey, Sousuke.

337
00:17:51,958 --> 00:17:53,208
Uh, yes?

338
00:17:53,291 --> 00:17:54,500
[KANAME]
I promise I won't get angry;

339
00:17:54,583 --> 00:17:56,458
I just want a straight answer.

340
00:17:56,541 --> 00:17:58,125
[SOUSUKE] I take it you want
to know what coincidence

341
