it was that brought me here.

342
00:18:01,000 --> 00:18:02,000
[KANAME groans]

343
00:18:02,083 --> 00:18:04,708
[KANAME]
Yeah, yeah, I get it.

344
00:18:04,791 --> 00:18:07,041
Then, as someone who also
just happened to be here,

345
00:18:07,125 --> 00:18:08,041
can I ask you something?

346
00:18:08,125 --> 00:18:09,708
What's that?

347
00:18:09,791 --> 00:18:12,125
[KANAME] You've lived overseas
for a long time, right?

348
00:18:12,208 --> 00:18:14,333
