at your other schools?

349
00:18:14,416 --> 00:18:17,458
[SOUSUKE] Yes. I enjoyed
peaceful days like this one.

350
00:18:17,541 --> 00:18:19,166
[KANAME]
Okay... But aren't you sad

351
