355
00:18:29,458 --> 00:18:30,541
Do you have a girl?

356
00:18:30,625 --> 00:18:31,916
[SOUSUKE]
A girl?

357
00:18:32,000 --> 00:18:34,291
[KANAME] A girlfriend!
A lover, someone like that.

358
00:18:34,375 --> 00:18:36,708
[SOUSUKE] No, I... don't have
any friends of that nature.

359
00:18:36,791 --> 00:18:39,625
[KANAME]
Hmm... Is that so...?

360
00:18:39,708 --> 00:18:41,791
[SOUSUKE] According to my
colleague-- I mean, my friend,

361
00:18:41,875 --> 00:18:44,125
