quite what to make

364
00:18:47,791 --> 00:18:49,458
of some of the things he says.

365
00:18:49,541 --> 00:18:52,416
[KANAME laughs]

366
00:18:52,500 --> 00:18:55,666
Your friend's a funny guy,
you know that?

367
00:18:55,750 --> 00:18:57,000
You know what he means?

368
00:18:57,083 --> 00:18:58,250
[KANAME]
Yeah!

369
00:18:58,333 --> 00:19:00,791
I mean, you are a bit
of an odd bird, Sousuke.

370
00:19:00,875 --> 00:19:01,833
Odd bird?

371
00:19:01,916 --> 00:19:04,416
