extremely odd.

372
00:19:04,500 --> 00:19:09,125
[KANAME giggles]

373
00:19:09,208 --> 00:19:10,708
[KANAME]
But maybe...

374
00:19:10,791 --> 00:19:14,250
Even with that rare
personality of yours,

375
00:19:14,333 --> 00:19:17,666
