to you on the way home? Hmm?

407
00:21:06,416 --> 00:21:07,875
[KANAME]
No, nothing!

408
00:21:07,958 --> 00:21:09,750
[KYOKO]
Nothing between you and Sousuke?

409
00:21:09,833 --> 00:21:12,666
[KANAME]
